Scrape FanGraphs.com Guts!

Source: R/fangraphs.R
fg_guts.Rd

This function allows you to scrape the historical, season-by-season wOBA and FIP constants and coefficients at FanGraphs.com.

fg_guts()

Examples

fg_guts()
